              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Serum 10 by SkinCeuticals</strong><br>
                Defend against environmental damage and brighten your complexion with this lightweight vitamin C
                antioxidant serum. It helps protect dry skin while enhancing radiance and smoothing uneven texture.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Cell Cycle Catalyst</strong><br>
                Boost your skin’s natural renewal process with this advanced treatment. It improves skin clarity,
                smooths rough texture, and helps refine pores for a softer, more luminous complexion.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
